---

praxis builds on the ideas and structure of prior open-source teaching skills:

- The workspace/mission model and spaced-retrieval session loop derive from
  Matt Pocock's /teach skill (MIT) and Tanish Girotra's spaced-retrieval fork
  (MIT). Reused with thanks.
- The deep-mode mastery-gate concept (Bloom's-taxonomy progression with
  multi-criteria verification) is inspired by adamos486's /teach skill. The
  pedagogy is reimplemented from first principles here, not copied.
